dth\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/16F1E/production/_100728939_indexpic7.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/16F1E/production/_100728939_indexpic7.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"The animals lie in a field together\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">CYNTHIA BENNETT</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">施茜娅热爱摄影，一对宠物正好成为她的模特。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我深信，巴路把亨利当成妈妈了。”施茜娅说：“最初几个月，巴路会揉着亨利找奶喝……”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">施茜娅甚至认为，巴路可能以为自己是只狗。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“如果它看到其他狗，它也会走向它，但见到猫就会无视。它究竟知不知道自己是什么动物呢？真有趣。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">亨利与巴路在一起、巴路骑在亨利身上、或追在亨利身边跑的照片与影片，在社交网站上大受欢迎。</p><p><br/></p>','亨利与巴路有很多共通点 ── 同样曾经陷入困境最终获救，现在也都同样喜欢在户外活动。然而在粉丝眼中这对好友的','新闻',4,3,'images/20180407233410_40.jpg'),(19,'阿大的','2018-04-07 23:34:40.799348','2018-04-07 23:34:40.799414','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">亨利与巴路有很多共通点 ── 同样曾经陷入困境最终获救，现在也都同样喜欢在户外活动。然而在粉丝眼中这对好友的特别之处，在于它们竟是一猫一狗。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在美国科罗拉多州的优美山水背景下，这对不寻常的好友的画面，在社交网站上吸引了大批粉丝，数以十万计的人追踪了它们的instagram。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43000262\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">被逼弃养七年后 美国女孩与小狗的意外重逢</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-40393721\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">它在台上懒懒躺下 就成了世界最丑狗狗</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对它们的主人施茜娅（Cynthia Bennett）及安德鲁（Andre Sibilsky）而言，这样的受欢迎程度很不真实。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1261C/production/_100729257_photojan0574306am.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1261C/production/_100729257_photojan0574306am.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"Cat lying on top of dog&#39;s head in front of mountain landscape\" width=\"549\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">CYNTHIA BENNETT</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">巴路总爱伏在亨利的头上。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">施茜娅与安德鲁分别来自新罕布什尔州及德克萨斯州，在波士顿相识。这对情侣说，彼此都是热爱大自然，注定要离开市中心的繁忙生活。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我们想一路往西，靠近更宏伟的山脉，来到了科罗拉多。我们随兴而行，没有什么计划可言。”施茜娅向BBC表示。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他们时常远足，找到住处安定下来后，领养了一只小狗“亨利”，一只高大瘦长的德国牧羊犬、哈士奇、拳师犬、斯塔福郡斗牛犬及澳洲牧羊犬混种。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/A200/production/_100727414_photomar0693055am.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/A200/production/_100727414_photomar0693055am.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"The couple pose for a selfie in a tent with the two animals\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">CYNTHIA BENNETT</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">宠物受到欢迎，令这对情侣能够追寻他们所喜爱的户外生活。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“它比其他同龄犬只身型大一倍。当我走进领养所一看到它，它就扑入我怀中，舒服地躺着。”施茜娅笑着说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我和安德鲁当时就知道，是它了。我觉得是它选择了我们。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">亨利出生在街头，后被动物拯救组织收容，由一些收容机构弃养、人道毁灭机率较高的州份，转移至环境较佳的州份。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">具有好动犬种血统的亨利，很快就爱上了长途远足。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">收养亨利一年后，施茜娅觉得自己的社交网站帐号全被它的照片占据，决定为亨利开设一个属于它自己的帐号。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/C53C/production/_100729405_og.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/C53C/production/_100729405_og.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"Beautiful lake and mountain landscape with dog exploring\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; fo