ass=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/16F1E/production/_100728939_indexpic7.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/16F1E/production/_100728939_indexpic7.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"The animals lie in a field together\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">CYNTHIA BENNETT</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">施茜娅热爱摄影，一对宠物正好成为她的模特。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我深信，巴路把亨利当成妈妈了。”施茜娅说：“最初几个月，巴路会揉着亨利找奶喝……”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">施茜娅甚至认为，巴路可能以为自己是只狗。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“如果它看到其他狗，它也会走向它，但见到猫就会无视。它究竟知不知道自己是什么动物呢？真有趣。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">亨利与巴路在一起、巴路骑在亨利身上、或追在亨利身边跑的照片与影片，在社交网站上大受欢迎。</p><p><br/></p>','亨利与巴路有很多共通点 ── 同样曾经陷入困境最终获救，现在也都同样喜欢在户外活动。然而在粉丝眼中这对好友的','小说',5,3,'images/20180407233440_76.jpg'),(20,'韩国总统是否注定难善终','2018-04-07 23:35:37.750533','2018-04-07 23:35:37.750558','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首尔中央地方法院4月6日对韩国前总统朴槿惠案进行一审宣判，朴槿惠因涉嫌滥用权力及胁迫等罪名被判有期徒刑24年，并被处以180亿韩元（相当于1700万美元）罚款。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">朴槿惠本人并未出庭。在检方提出的18项指控中，朴槿惠被判16项有罪，其中大多数罪名与受贿及胁迫有关，此前，她曾否认所有指控。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果服满刑期，朴槿惠出狱时将是90岁。朴槿惠可在7天内提出上诉。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/857D/production/_100737143_045978210.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/857D/production/_100737143_045978210.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"South Koreans watch as the verdict is broadcast live\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AFP/GETTY</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">韩国民众观看审判直播。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">受“亲信干政”风波影响，朴槿惠于2017年3月10日下台，是韩国第一位被弹劾下台的总统。同年3月31日，朴槿惠被批捕。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“亲信干政门”的另一主角、朴槿惠密友崔顺实已于2月18日被判处20年有期徒刑及180亿韩元（相当于1700万美元）罚款。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-39231836\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">人物：韩国首位被弹劾下台的总统朴槿惠</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/indepth/2015/11/151122_jim_young_sam_orb\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">韩国前总统金泳三逝世 回顾其“功过”</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">朴槿惠为韩国第18任总统，也是第11位韩国总统。在她之前的10位总统中，有1位遇刺身亡，1位自杀，3人被迫下台，2人被判刑，2人近亲被判刑，1人尚在羁押中，可以说很少有人得以“全身而退”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">多位学者向BBC中文表示，出现这种现象的原因与韩国政治制度架构及政治环境有很大关系。</p><hr class=\"story-body__line\" style=\"background-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border: 0px; color: rgb(219, 219, 219); height: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 16px; width: 591.562px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"/><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">历任韩国总统的政治结局</strong></p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第1-3任：李承晚，结局：被迫辞职，流亡美国。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第4任：尹潽善，结局：朴正熙发动军事政变，被迫下台。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第5-9任：朴正熙，结局：遇刺身亡。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第10任：崔圭夏，结局：军事政变后被迫辞职。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第11-12任：全斗焕，结局：卸任后被判无期徒刑，后被特赦。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第13任：卢泰愚，结局：卸任后被判17年有期徒刑，后被特赦。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第14任：金泳三，结局：任期内因97年亚洲金融危机接受检方调查。其子在其任期尾声因受贿被判刑。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第15任：金大中，结局：三个儿子因受贿或逃税被判刑。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第16任：卢武铉，结局：涉嫌腐败、自杀。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第17任：李明博，结局：羁押中。</p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p>第18任：朴槿惠，结局：一审被判有期徒刑24年。</p></li></ul><hr class=\"story-body__line\" style=\"background-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border: 0px; color: rgb(219, 219, 219); height: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 16px; width: 591.562px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"/><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总统权力缺乏制衡</h2><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/148CD/production/_100737148_april06supportersofformerpresidentparkgeun-hyeparticipateinarallyinfrontoftheseoulcentraldistrictcourtonapril62018inseoulsouthkorea.theseoulcentraldistrictcourtsentencedformersouthko.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/148CD/production/_100737148_april06supportersofformerpresidentparkgeun-hyeparticipateinarallyinfrontoftheseoulcentraldistrictcourtonapril62018inseoulsouthkorea.theseoulcentraldistrictcourtsentencedformersouthko.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"朴槿惠支持者\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">朴槿惠一审获罪同时，支持朴槿惠的民众在法院外集会，声援朴槿惠。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">韩国首尔大学政治外交系教授康元泽称，韩国总统权力高度集中，缺乏制衡，导致他们在位时权力很大，可以“为所欲为”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据韩国法律，总统是国家元首，同时也是政府首脑，可以任命国务总理及各行政部门长官。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">康元泽认为，由于韩国总统享有很大程度的人事任命权，作为最重要的政治领袖，所有人都需为总统“尽心尽力”，因此容易导致权力滥用及腐败。“有时即使并非其本意，其亲属及周边人也会遇到同样问题”，他说。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总统单一任期制</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">韩国宪法规定，韩国总统任期5年，不得连任。康元泽表示，正是由于这种制度，韩国总统总是无法避免“强力开始，跛脚鸭结束”的命运。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“跛脚鸭（lame duck）”多用于形容因任期即将届满而失去政治影响力的政治人物。康元泽称，对于有问题的总统，韩国检方往往在其任期中便掌握一些证据，但只有在其执政后期、权力式微之际才会开始调查，此前“则一直要看总统眼色行事”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国政治学者吴强认为，韩国司法的相对独立也是使得这些政治人物的非法行为浮出水面的重要因素。但他强调，虽然韩国检方的行动“可圈可点”，但对于民主政治来说，更重要的是议会与立法体系的制衡。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">裙带资本主义</h2><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/6255/production/_100737152_protestasseoulcourtdeliversverdictonformerpresidentpark.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/6255/production/_100737152_protestasseoulcourtdeliversverdictonformerpresidentpark.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"朴槿惠\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">检方提出的18项指控中朴槿惠被判16项有罪，其中大多数罪名与受贿及胁迫有关。图为朴槿惠支持者在宣判当天参加集会。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">吴强称，民主基础不够牢固也是韩国政治变动较频繁的重要原因。“如果没有美国式民主传统，很多国家实行集权式总统制时往往容易滋生腐败问题”，他称。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">吴强指出，韩国政治体制带有很强的“裙带资本主义（Cronycapitalism）”色彩。在这种情景中，政商之间往往关系密切。他认为，裙带资本主义曾一度支撑韩国经济的高速发展，但也掩盖其政治、社会很多问题，民主制度因此没有充分变革。而历任韩国总统们往往都是是裙带资本主义的“代理人和牺牲品”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在朴槿惠的16项罪名中，便包括其向三星、乐天、现代汽车等韩国财阀集团索贿、受贿等内容。</p><p><br/></p>','首尔中央地方法院4月6日对韩国前总统朴槿惠案进行一审宣判，朴槿惠因涉嫌滥用权力及胁迫等罪名被判有期徒刑24年','小说',13,3,'images/20180407233537_85.jpg'),(21,'日本动画大师高畑勋逝世','2018-04-07 23:36:54.499864','2018-04-07 23:36:54.499890','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">日本动漫导演高畑勋5日在东京都内医院去世，享年82岁。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高畑勋执导《萤火虫之墓》、《阿尔卑斯山的少女》等20多部知名影片。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1985年他与动画宫崎骏共同创立传奇的动画工作室——吉卜力工作室。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高畑勋与宫崎骏被媒体描述成“亦敌亦友”关系。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/fooc-38417268\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">记者来鸿：日本动画大片火爆中国的玄机</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与宫崎骏共创吉卜力</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高畑勋是在1968年拍摄处女作《太阳王子·霍尔斯大冒险》时与宫崎骏合作。因此外界认为，是他发现了宫崎骏，也是他最早启用的音乐家久石让。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但高畑勋2014年向中国《南方周末》杂志表示：“人们认为是我发现了他，其实不是这样。确实，只要我当导演就让他担任最核心的主创，这段时间蛮长的，这期间他自己学会了导演技巧，倒不是我教的。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高畑勋与宫崎骏在1985年进一步加深合作，两人合作创立了著名的吉卜力工作室，高畑勋同年担任了《天空之城》的制作人。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在吉卜力工作室，高畑勋执导了多部享誉全球的动画电影：1988年反战主题的《萤火虫之墓》（港名《再见萤火虫》）讲述二战时两个孤儿的故事，广受赞誉，被认为是他最佳作品；2013年的《辉夜姬物语》获得了奥斯卡最佳动画长片提名；2016年以80岁高龄出任《红海龟》的制作人，这是他参与的吉卜力工作室的最后一部动画电影。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/0674/production/_100725610_hi034729846.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/0674/production/_100725610_hi034729846.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"宫崎骏\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AFP/GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">高畑勋与宫崎骏一同创办吉卜力</span></figcaption></figure></p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">亦敌亦友</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高畑勋与宫崎骏被媒体描述成“亦敌亦友”关系。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">两人多年合作，但在创作理念上有所分歧，高畑勋不同意宫崎骏采取的“代入式情感投射”，只让观众从主人公的视点来观察世界，很难看清整个世界。他则更倾向于“体谅式情感投射”的创作方式，“应该拍摄给观众客观性视点、让观众保持判断力和理性的作品。不是说让观众与主人公同化，而是冷静地明白，自己虽然与主人公不同，但能够体谅他的情感。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国美术学者龚念、杨晓林在《当代电影》杂志上曾评价，高畑勋的现实主义作品是深刻自然地讲述日常生活，他的动画更多是面向琐细的生活涓流，相对于宫崎骏的神奇瑰丽，高畑勋动画平实而又生活化。他的作品洞悉人性冷暖、笔调深邃、关注社会现实、哲学意蕴浓厚。他用超现实化的童话手法与现实化的散文式叙事手段编织了一曲平凡而感伤的岁月之歌。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对中国失望</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高畑勋在《南方周末》的采访中曾表示他的动画创作受到中国画的影响。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他说，“我喜欢的正是中国水墨画里的留白……大幅留白很符合日本人的审美观，所以我拍《辉夜姬物语》时就学了留白。留白饱含真意。”甚至，中国上海美术电影制片厂早期的作品，“《小蝌蚪找妈妈》，看的时候我都傻了，没想到竟然能做出这样的作品。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1984年，高畑勋和宫崎骏首次来到中国，并访问上海美术电影制片厂，但后者只关心员工收入分配的问题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高畑勋说：“宫崎骏对中国的失望无以复加。我在这一点上也是如此。因为我们对上海美术电影制片厂是很尊敬的，没想到上海美术电影制片厂高层却只关心这个。”</p><p><br/></p>','日本动漫导演高畑勋5日在东京都内医院去世，享年82岁。\n\n高畑勋执导《萤火虫之墓》、《阿尔卑斯山的少女》等2','新闻',19,3,'images/20180407233654_48.jpg'),(22,'扎克伯格：我才不会从脸书辞职','2018-04-07 23:38:11.344332','2018-04-07 23:38:11.344356','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">围绕脸书（Facebook）的风波还在发酵，脸书创始人马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）周三召开电话记者会时坚称，他仍是领导公司的最佳人选。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">会上扎克伯格表示，在打造像脸书这种“史无前例”的事物时，“有些事情是你时会搞砸的”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我认为人们应该要求我们负责的是，我们要从自己的错误中吸取教训。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">目前扎克伯格身兼脸书首席执行官与董事会主席职位。被问及公司是否有讨论他的职位变动时，他回答称：“据我所知没有！”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而在一个月前，可能没有几个人会提出这种问题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但近期关于第三方不当收集数据、假新闻、舆论宣传等问题的报道使得外界开始质疑扎克伯格的领导能力，一些人认为脸书可能已经成长到一定程度，超过他控制范围了。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“根据架构，他不可能被解雇-他只能辞职”</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">纽约养老基金主管斯科特·斯特林格（Scott Stringer）表示，扎克伯格应于本周辞职。斯特林格主管的基金持有的脸书股票价值约10亿美元。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-42764202\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">脸书打假：优先推送用户认定的可靠新闻源</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-41425438\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">扎克伯格喊冤：凭什么都说我&quot;反特朗普&quot;？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-42828323\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">索罗斯：谷歌和脸书给民主带来威胁</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">斯特林格向美国电视频道CNBC指出，脸书拥有20亿用户，但自己却处于未知的环境中，没能为用户提供满意的服务，也没能让用户感到自己的数据是安全的。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他呼吁扎克伯格下台，从而让脸书开启“提高声誉的第二篇章”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">财经记者费里克斯·萨尔蒙（Felix Salmon）日前撰文写道，“他（扎克伯格）领导的不仅仅是一个几乎可以接触到世界上所有人的机构”，“多亏了金融工程，他现在还拥有大股东投票权，并且控制着董事会，因此他可以不对任何人负责。根据架构，他不可能被解雇-他只能辞职。这正是他现在应该做的。”</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“一个经常被批评缺乏同理心的男人”</h2><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/436C/production/_100706271_mediaitem100706270.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/436C/production/_100706271_mediaitem100706270.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"A lit sign at Facebook HQ\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AFP/GETTY</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">扎克伯格说“删除脸书”运动影响有限。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关于负面舆论和“删除脸书”运动带来的真正损失，扎克伯格的回答让我们了解到更多一点信息。目前为止他的回答是：不多。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他说，“据我们观察，目前并没有什么实质性影响”。随即他又补充道，“但你们看，这并不好！”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于是电话记者会，我们并不能得知，在同一个房间里，扎克伯格的团队给他提供了多大程度的指导。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但对经常被批评缺乏同理心的扎克伯格来说，他在近一小时的记者会上表现得很强劲。记者会刚一结束，脸书的股价便上涨3%。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下周他可能会面临更严峻的情形，他将前往华盛顿在国会作证，这次他需要面对镜头。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这次记者会或许正是一场理想的彩排。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来几个月，随着以联邦贸易委员会（FTC）为首的机构对脸书调查逐步展开，以及对脸书如何操作公众数据的调查不断深入，围绕扎克伯格领导权的声音可能会发生戏剧性变化。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果脸书被认为未尽到应有责任，并被处以巨额罚款，那么该公司将会在人事调整上面临更大压力。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">截至目前，除作出道歉及承认判断不当外，扎克伯格还告诉记者，公司并没有因“剑桥分析”事件开除任何员工。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">责任在于他，他说。事实上可能也的确如此。</p><p><br/></p>','围绕脸书（Facebook）的风波还在发酵，脸书创始人马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）周三召','新闻',5,3,'images/20180407233811_50.jpg'),(23,'缩小职场男女薪资鸿沟','2018-04-07 23:40:03.751279','2018-04-07 23:40:03.751305','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国要求2018年4月开始，雇佣人员数量超过280人以上的公共部门和私营公司必须公开披露男女薪资中位数和整体性别收入差距。同时公司有必要制定相应计划以缩小性别收入差距。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国时间周三晚为交答卷的最后期限。至少有约1万家公司在此前提交了数据，有1000家公司将在最后一天交卷。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">公开披露的数据显示，所有公司的平均性别薪资差在9.7%左右。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据已提交数据的公司现状显示，有78%的公司多付男性薪水，14%多付女性薪水。有8%的公司称他们没有性别薪资差距。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那企业实际可以做些什么来改变现状？</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/ukchina/simp/uk_life/2014/12/141226_life_uk_salary\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">辛辛苦苦又一年 英打工族能挣多少钱？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk-42855913\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">回应男女薪酬不平等 六名BBC男主持人接受减薪</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这有八个建议：</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 提供更好的育儿福利</h2><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/11B34/production/_100700527_gettyimages-684059604.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/11B34/production/_100700527_gettyimages-684059604.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"childcare\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">许多女性在反社交的工作时间里无法获得适当的托儿服务。薪酬高的管理职位通常需要员工延长或拥有灵活的工作时间，这使许多女性因为从事常规的工作而接受低薪工作。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Equal Pay Portal的创始人希拉·外德（Sheila Wild）说：“提供育儿服务能让你走出去上班，这使你能晋升拿到一份薪水较高的工作”。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 企业写更好的招聘广告</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">许多招聘广告都没有提到它们的工作对女性是友善的。例如，只有不到10％的广告提及灵活工作时间。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国特许人事发展协会（CIPD）首席执行官彼得·奇斯（Peter Cheese）认为，招聘广告可以写得更好。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“有很多证据表明，用于描述工作的许多词语无意中可能会将女性排除在外，或使她们认为这项工作更适合男性，这就加深了对男性的刻板印象。”</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 薪酬透明</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">公布性别工资差距可能是提高薪酬透明度的开始。许多女性很可能不知道男性同事挣得比她们多。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/10BF8/production/_100700686_gettyimages-639072334.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/10BF8/production/_100700686_gettyimages-639072334.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"man interviews woman\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">自2016年8月以来，美国马萨诸塞州的工人在这方面拥有一些权利。而且，她们不必再透露她们上一份工作的报酬。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有证据表明雇主根据女性上一份工作提供现有工作的薪水。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4. 目标</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一些公司已经公布了招聘目标。劳埃德银行集团（Lloyds Banking Group）承诺，到2020年，女性担任高级职位的比例将达到40％。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然而，英国女性董事（Women on Boards UK）的总经理菲奥娜·哈索恩（Fiona Hathorn）认为，这样的目标是不现实的。例如，一家试图招女工程师的公司可能会发现市场上的女毕业生太少。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她说：“确定女性担任领导职位的目标是明智的，但我们需要理智的目标，而其中一些目标可能会疏远男性。”</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5. 支付女性更多薪水</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">工资低不是没问题，毕竟同工不同酬是非法的。但支付女性更多薪水有助于解决问题。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/7EF4/production/_100700523_gettyimages-dv1693021.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/7EF4/production/_100700523_gettyimages-dv1693021.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"woman and man with piles of cash\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这个问题更多是关于女性的晋升、保持工作热情和进取心的培养。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6. 更好的培训</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">许多专家提倡为了摆脱管理人员潜在的偏见，应该给员工提供更好的培训。有高级职称的员工可能需要更努力地鼓励女性寻求晋升空间。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">CIPD的奇斯说：“很多男性在未准备好时就会争取职位。相反，许多女性不会这么做，她们认为自己还没有准备好，但她们实际已经准备好。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我们必须更好地培训直线经理，以便他们能够了解自己如何看待或处理对女性的偏见。”</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">7. 文化</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">CIPD称，高级管理人员应该有责任改变工作场所的文化。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">奇斯说：“我深信，现在是领导层做出行动的时候了，要搞清楚，高层的论调是什么？领导层对性别薪酬差距有什么看法？他们是否试图对发生在公司的令人不舒服的真相充耳不闻？ 还是他们对此持坦诚和开放的态度？”</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">8. 运动</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">鼓励女孩在年轻的时候多运动可以增强她们的自尊心。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1656C/production/_100700519_gettyimages-598217390.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1656C/production/_100700519_gettyimages-598217390.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"boy and girl playing football\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">和男孩一起踢足球，可以激发女性争取更好的工作吗？</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国女性董事（Women on Boards UK）的哈索恩（Fiona Hathorn）说，12岁前，男孩和女孩应该一起踢足球。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她说：“参加国际级别体育赛事的女性被办公室里男性视为领导者。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">参加运动还可以改变女性对自己的期望。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“四岁的年轻女孩相信她们可以做任何事，但到了六岁，她们就有不同的看法，”她补充道。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“到12岁前，女孩的身体和男孩一样强壮，所以他们应该参加同样的运动。”</p><p><br/></p>','英国要求2018年4月开始，雇佣人员数量超过280人以上的公共部门和私营公司必须公开披露男女薪资中位数和整体','新闻',2,3,'images/20180407234003_70.jpg'),(24,'中美亮底牌后开始互动','2018-04-07 23:41:46.193841','2018-04-07 23:41:46.193867','<p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 28px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中美之间的贸易摩擦升级，美国宣布或向中国产品征税后，中国随即有所反击，同样计划向对方部分产品征收关税，不过中美双方均表示希望以谈判化解危机。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国总统特朗普表示，并不是与中国进行贸易战。白宫首席经济顾问库德洛（Larry Kudlow）认为中国会在贸易问题上让步，与美国达成协议。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">欧美股市暂时未有受到很大冲击，其中美股4月4日开市时低开，但在库德洛发表上述言论后，反弹以高1%收市。</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43595219\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美贸易战会将中国推向“失落的二十年”？</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43553945\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美战略性贸易摩擦：断定贸易战到来为时尚早</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43531738\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美贸易战：中国的余地和特朗普的目的</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43610276\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美贸易战阴影下的忧心者样本：美国红酒</a></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(30, 30, 30);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: inherit;line-height: 1.5;margin: 32px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">会否谈判？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">北京早前已多次表明不想有贸易战，但也不怕真的打起来。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中国驻美大使崔天凯与美国代理国务卿沙利文（John Sullivan）会面，历时约一小时，就经贸问题等交换意见。双方称有关会面是在华府宣布有关关税措施前已经安排。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中方指，崔天凯重申了中美经贸问题上的立场，要求美方及早摒弃单边主义和贸易保护主义的做法，停止对华301调查，通过对话协商的方式同中方解决有关分歧。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">崔天凯对记者表示，中方依然倾向以谈判解决问题，但需要双方参与，会留意美国的做法。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;clear: both;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block;position: relative\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/4D49/production/_100558791_gettyimages-936577972.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/4D49/production/_100558791_gettyimages-936577972.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"特朗普\" width=\"976\" height=\"800\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto;max-width: 100%;user-select: none;width: 616.203px;transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in;display: block\"/><span style=\"color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">图片版权</span><span style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(236, 236, 236);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 0.875rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: 0.25px;line-height: 1.14286;padding: 3px 8px 1px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);bottom: 0px;position: absolute;right: 0px\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">路透社引述不具名美国经贸官员指，美国亦寻求以谈判解决与中方贸易的深层矛盾，但拒绝透露会否有更高级别的官员会晤。路透社分析，4月20-22日在华盛顿举行的国际货币基金及世界银行会议，可能是其中一个机会，让中美双方在场边讨论有关争议。</p><p><a class=\"off-screen jump-link\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43651067#jump-linkhttps://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&ref_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-43632315&tfw_creator=BBCNews&tfw_site=BBCNews\" style=\"font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">跳过 Twitter 帖子 用户名 @realDonaldTrump</a><twitterwidget class=\"twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered\" id=\"twitter-widget-0\" data-tweet-id=\"981492087328792577\" style=\";utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#39;#2AA9E0&#39; d=&#39;M24.029 3.32c-.882.391-1.829.655-2.824.774 1.016-.608 1.795-1.572 2.162-2.72-.95.563-2.003.973-3.122 1.192-.896-.955-2.175-1.552-3.589-1.552-2.715 0-4.917 2.202-4.917 4.917 0 .385.044.761.128 1.121-4.087-.205-7.709-2.163-10.134-5.137-.423.726-.666 1.57-.666 2.471 0 1.706.868 3.21 2.188 4.093-.806-.026-1.565-.247-2.228-.615v.062c0 2.382 1.695 4.369 3.944 4.821-.413.111-.847.172-1.295.172-.317 0-.625-.03-.925-.088.625 1.953 2.442 3.375 4.593 3.414-1.683 1.319-3.802 2.104-6.106 2.104-.396 0-.788-.023-1.173-.068 2.176 1.396 4.76 2.209 7.537 2.209 9.043 0 13.989-7.492 13.989-13.989l-.015-.636c.96-.693 1.794-1.559 2.453-2.545z&#39;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#39;);background-position: 16px 13px;border: 0px solid rgb(255, 255, 255);border-radius: 4px;font-weight: initial;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;visibility: visible;display: block;position: static;transform: rotate(0deg);max-width: 100%;width: 500px;min-width: 220px\"><blockquote class=\"Tweet h-entry js-tweetIdInfo subject expanded\" cite=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577\" data-tweet-id=\"981492087328792577\" data-scribe=\"section:subject\" style=\";padding: 0px;list-style: none;border: none\"><a class=\"TweetAuthor-avatar Identity-avatar u-linkBlend\" data-scribe=\"element:user_link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" aria-label=\"Donald J. Trump (用户名: realDonaldTrump)\" style=\"background-color: transparent;outline: 0px;-webkit-box-flex: 0;flex: 0 0 auto;height: 36px;font-weight: inherit\"><img class=\"Avatar Avatar--edge\" data-scribe=\"element:avatar\" data-src-2x=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/874276197357596672/kUuht00m_bigger.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src-1x=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/874276197357596672/kUuht00m_normal.jpg\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/874276197357596672/kUuht00m_bigger.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;max-width: 100%;max-height: 100%;border-radius: 50%\"/></a><a class=\"TweetAuthor-link Identity u-linkBlend\" data-scribe=\"element:user_link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" aria-label=\"Donald J. Trump (用户名: realDonaldTrump)\" style=\"background-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;-webkit-box-align: start;align-items: flex-start;font-weight: inherit\"><span style=\"display: flex;-webkit-box-align: center;align-items: center;min-width: 0px\"><span class=\"TweetAuthor-name Identity-name customisable-highlight\" title=\"Donald J. Trump\" data-scribe=\"element:name\" style=\"font-weight: 700;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;padding-right: 4px\">Donald J. Trump</span><span data-scribe=\"element:verified_badge\" style=\"position: static;-webkit-box-flex: 0;flex: 0 0 auto;padding-right: 4px\"><span style=\"position: absolute !important;overflow: hidden !important;width: 1px !important;height: 1px !important;padding: 0px !important;border: 0px !important;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px) !important\">✔</span></span></span><span class=\"TweetAuthor-screenName Identity-screenName\" title=\"@realDonaldTrump\" data-scribe=\"element:screen_name\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: rgb(105, 120, 130);font-size: 14px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;flex-shrink: 1\">@realDonaldTrump</span></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577\" data-scribe=\"element:logo\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(43, 123, 185);outline: 0px\"></a><p class=\"Tweet-text e-entry-title\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;list-style: none;border: none;white-space: pre-wrap;cursor: text;word-wrap: break-word;direction: ltr\">We are not in a trade war with China, that war was lost many years ago by the foolish, or incompetent, people who represented the U.S. Now we have a Trade Deficit of $500 Billion a year, with Intellectual Property Theft of another $300 Billion. We cannot let this continue!</p><a class=\"u-linkBlend u-url customisable-highlight long-permalink\" data-datetime=\"2018-04-04T11:22:03+0000\" data-scribe=\"element:full_timestamp\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577\" style=\"background-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-weight: inherit\">下午7:22 - 2018年4月4日</a><ul class=\"Tweet-actions Tweet-action--newsActions list-paddingleft-2\" data-scribe=\"component:actions\" role=\"menu\" aria-label=\"法推行动\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><a class=\"Tweet-action--heart TweetAction TweetAction--heartEdge\" title=\"赞\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/like?tweet_id=981492087328792577\" data-scribe=\"component:actions\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(105, 120, 130);outline: 0px;display: flex;-webkit-box-align: center;align-items: center\"><span data-scribe=\"element:heart_count\" style=\"display: inline-block;font-size: 14px;vertical-align: text-bottom;margin-left: 3px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;min-width: 0px\">13.8万</span></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"Tweet-action--replyEdge TweetAction TweetAction--replyEdge\" title=\"在 Twitter 上查看对话\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577\" data-scribe=\"component:news\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(105, 120, 130);outline: 0px;display: flex;-webkit-box-align: center;align-items: center\"><span data-scribe=\"element:conversation_text\" style=\"display: inline-block;font-size: 14px;vertical-align: text-bottom;margin-left: 3px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;min-width: 0px\">6.53万 人正在讨论这个</span></a></p></li></ul></blockquote><a href=\"https://support.twitter.com/articles/20175256\" class=\"Icon Icon--informationCircleWhite js-inViewportScribingTarget\" title=\"Twitter 广告信息与隐私\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(43, 123, 185);outline: 0px;display: inline-block;height: 18px;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: contain;vertical-align: text-bottom;width: 18px\"><span style=\"position: absolute !important;overflow: hidden !important;width: 1px !important;height: 1px !important;padding: 0px !important;border: 0px !important;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px) !important\">Twitter 广告信息与隐私</span></a></twitterwidget></p><p id=\"jump-linkhttps://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-43632315&amp;tfw_creator=BBCNews&amp;tfw_site=BBCNews\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">结尾 Twitter 帖子 用户名 @realDonaldTrump</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国总统特朗普在推特（Twitter）表示，美国并不是与中国进行贸易战，只是不容许继续有贸易逆差及侵权的情况。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">白宫首席经济顾问库德洛（Larry Kudlow）认为，最终中国会退下来，与美国合作并达成协议。他的言论让美国股市由低开后反弹。</p><h2 style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(30, 30, 30);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: inherit;line-height: 1.5;margin: 32px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">甚么产品被征收关税？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中国商务部发的公告表示，计划向106种美国产品进口商品征收25%关税，当中包括原产于美国的大豆、小麦、鲜冷肉类等农产品、部分汽车、烟草、威士忌、高粱产品、冷冻橙汁、化学品、部分飞机、塑料产品等。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">公告称：“涉及2017年中国自美国进口金额约500亿美元，最终措施及生效时间将另行公告。”</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17);clear: both;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block;position: relative\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/7622/production/_100524203_34575.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/7622/production/_100524203_34575.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"美国犹他州詹森市的艾斯克兰迪农场正在收割燕麦。\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(189, 189, 189);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto;max-width: 100%;user-select: none;width: 616.203px;transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in;display: block\"/><span style=\"color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">图片版权</span><span style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(236, 236, 236);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 0.875rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: 0.25px;line-height: 1.14286;padding: 3px 8px 1px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);bottom: 0px;position: absolute;right: 0px\">CNS</span></span><figcaption style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 16px;vertical-align: baseline;visibility: visible\"><span style=\"color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">Image caption</span><span style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(236, 236, 236);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 0.75rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.33333;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block\">美国犹他州詹森市的艾斯克兰迪农场正在收割燕麦。评论认为，中国如果采取贸易反制措施，将使美国农业遭受严重打击。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">而中国声明中，针对的飞机为“空载重量超过15000公斤，但不超过45000公斤的飞机及其他航空器”，中国媒体进一步说明，这是涉及波音737系列和737 MAX 7，没有提及波音较新、利润较大的的737 MAX 8、9、10系列。不过中国提出的措施已令波音股价受压。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国则宣称拟向中国1300种中国产品征收25%关税，涉及的层面十分广泛，由焗炉、电视等家庭用品、半导体、通讯卫星、火箭发射台科技产品、医疗器械、药物疫苗、工业机器等等。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美方指责中国窃取知识产权，强迫美国公司与中国企业分享技术，认为目前拟定的关税已考虑到潜在对美国经济的损害，并相信能争取中国撤销其有害的行为、政策与措施。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">最终产品清单预料经过公众咨询和审视，约两个月后实行。</p><h2 style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(30, 30, 30);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: inherit;line-height: 1.5;margin: 32px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">真的会爆发贸易战？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国数字显示，美国去年与中国的货品及服务交易，超过7000亿美元。双方今次拟定的关税措施所针对的产品，均是估计每年约500亿美元的交易额。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国商务部长威尔伯‧罗斯（Wilbur Ross）表示，中国针对的这批产品，只是占美国国民生产总值（GDP）的0.3% ，并不认为这会危害到美国经济。</p><p><figure class=\"media-portrait no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;clear: both;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block;position: relative\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/11B04/production/_100525427_us_china_trade_import_export_ws_chinese-nc.png\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/11B04/production/_100525427_us_china_trade_import_export_ws_chinese-nc.png\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"GRAPH\" width=\"640\" height=\"695\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto;max-width: 100%;user-select: none;width: 616.203px;transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in;display: block\"/></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国经济专家认为，相关措施目前规模尚未大到会撼动整体经济，但警告如果摩擦加剧会对商业活动构成更大风险。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">标准普尔分析认为，中国近年减少了对出口的依赖，这可以帮助减轻美国加征关税带来的影响。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2016年，中国整体出口货品中，有18.2%是出口至美国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">不过，标普高级经济师潘戴（Satyam Panday）表示，这种以牙还牙式的不稳定性动摇商界信心。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“为甚么我会在未有把握的时候投资呢？”他说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国商界组织呼吁两国尝试对话解</p><p><br/></p>','中美之间的贸易摩擦升级，美国宣布或向中国产品征税后，中国随即有所反击，同样计划向对方部分产品征收关税，不过中','小说',4,3,'images/20180407234146_85.jpg'),(25,'德国高速公路不限速','2018-04-07 23:43:25.752738','2018-04-07 23:43:25.752764','<p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">世界最早的封闭高速公路系统诞生于德国，但是现在世界上规模最大的高速公路系统在中国。德国高速公路以没有限速而闻名。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">截至2016年底，中国大陆高速公路的通车总里程突破13万公里（超过了美国），是世界上规模最大的高速公路系统。2016年，德国高速公路网的总长度为12,996公里，考虑到德国面积只相当于中国的1/30，因此德国是世界上高速公路最稠密和最长的国家之一。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/11/081127_motorway_50yrs.shtml\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">英国高速公路50年</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2007/06/070625_roadsafety.shtml\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">英国最危险公路在哪里？</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然德国高速公路没有法定限速，但根据每10万人为单位统计的交通事故死亡率，德国的交通死亡率为6.8，远低于美国的12.9。而中国以10万人为统计单位的交通死亡率高达18.8，不仅高于中等收入国家18.5的水平，而且达到高收入国家9.3比例的两倍。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">平均时速142公里</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国《独立报》记者布朗把德国的高速公路同美国做了比较，他认为德国高速公路是世界上驾车旅行最好的高速公路系统之一，同美国公路相比，德国公路上的靓车更多。他认为德国高速公路没有限速，高速公路上很少看到警察/警车也是德国系统优越的方面。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">准确地说，德国高速公路对一些车辆并没有联邦规定的限速，但是在城市，和标准低的公路，事故多发段和施工地区仍然有临时或常设的限速规定。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据2008年的一个统计，德国高速公路网52%的路段只有建议的最高速度，没有法定限速。15%的路段因为天气和交通情况有临时限速，33%的路段有常设限速规定。2006年德国对6车道高速公路的测量显示，在正常状态下德国高速公路上的平均车速为每小时142公里。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国高速公路一般都由多层水泥筑成，更适合高速行驶的需要。德国高速公路的路面经常定期经过检测，查看有无不规整或损毁。如果发现了上述情况，整个受影响的路面会被更换。许多美国人认为德国路面质量和公路养护优于美国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然没有法定限速，但德国高速公路的建议最高速度为每小时130公里，虽然超过此限并不违法，但发生交通事故时，超速驾车者要承担更大的事故责任。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在德国汽车保险公司一般的政策是，当汽车在每小时200公里速度行驶时发生车祸，即使在高速驾车者并无其他过错的情况下，保险公司的赔偿支付会大大减少，甚至完全不予赔偿。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/D5FA/production/_100687745_c29b7763-a923-4564-bb1e-e17a35a261d5.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/D5FA/production/_100687745_c29b7763-a923-4564-bb1e-e17a35a261d5.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"beijing\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">截至2016年底，中国大陆高速公路的通车总里程突破13万公里（超过了美国）是世界上规模最大的高速公路系统。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然现在德国高速公路不限速的路段在减少，一些德国人认为高速公路不限速是德国的弊端，他们责怪德国立法议员不作为，没有规定高速公路限速。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">交规和驾考更严格</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《独立报》把德国公路系统优于美国的原因总结为8个，除了不限速，德国驾车者更遵守交通规则。德国公路和美国大部分公路一样，超车在左边车道进行，右边车道正常行驶。在不超车的情况下，必须靠右行驶。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《独立报》认为，和美国的主要不同是，德国驾车者都严格遵守以上规则，而美国人则很少遵守。因为德国人更尊重这种规定，高速公路交通就能更顺畅。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国读者认为，美国人不太受车道约束，美国许多州允许从左或从右超车。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国汽车严格执行定期检查。定期检车有助于减少潜在危险车辆的数目，减少对驾车者和其他车辆的威胁。《独立报》说，美国一些州的车辆检查同德国的相比就像是开玩笑。德国全国保持统一标准，而美国的车检各州都不一样。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国驾车水平整体高于美国，是因为德国有更严格的驾照考试系统。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在德国考取驾照，报考者需要上很多驾驶课程，包括在实际高速公路上的驾驶课，体验真实的高速交通。另外驾车者要接受基本的急救训练，另外还要经过难度很高的多项选择笔试和路考。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果一切顺利，完成这个过程需要6个月事件，考试者要付出2000美元的代价。显然在德国驾车，需要有更多的决心和投入。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国公路交通倍受赞扬的另外一个原因是行车距离保持得比较好。《独立报》文章说，虽然在德国公路上警察不多，但是如果你没有和前面保持足够车距，就会受到严厉的罚款，罚款可高达450美元。在美国如果发生同样的情况，州警察如果眨一下眼睛就算不错了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国公路上的警察比美国少也被认为是德国公路系统的优点。《独立报》文章作者认为，警察会令一些驾车者感到紧张，即使他们没有做违法的事情。而在德国高速公路上，驾车者就很少会因为看到警察而紧张。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外一个优点是，德国道路系统免费行驶，没有收费站。目前德国唯一要付费的车辆是货车。一般驾车者不需要停车付费，但是这样也就减少了路途停车的次数。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/60CA/production/_100687742_ba3ef6af-9027-4435-8967-978f6da0d5df.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/60CA/production/_100687742_ba3ef6af-9027-4435-8967-978f6da0d5df.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"1930s autobahn\" width=\"766\" height=\"511\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">纳粹德国时期德国新修的高速公路被称为&quot;希特勒的公路&quot;，在纳粹宣传中被称为全民就业的典范工程。</span></figcaption></figure></p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高速公路始于德国</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国是世界上最早建设封闭高速公路系统的国家。1932年德国第一条高速公路在科隆和波恩之间修建完成，当时的科隆市长（未来的西德总理）阿登纳主持了高速公路开幕典礼。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">早在1920年代中期魏玛共和国就有建设专门供汽车使用的高速公路的计划，但因为缺乏经济支持和政治共识，高速公路项目在纳粹上台以前主要停留在计划阶段。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国航空界出于担心来自汽车交通的竞争，极力反对建立封闭的高速公路系统，连德国汽车协会对耗资巨大的高速公路也不热心。1933年希特勒上台后才改变了这个局面，因为希特勒认为铁路运输已经过时，公路运输是未来。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当时德国新修的高速公路被称为“希特勒的公路”，在纳粹宣传中被称为全民就业的典范工程。这实际上是德国工程师弗利兹·托特力主通过修建高速公路系统，振兴德国经济。他的主张被纳粹政权采纳，他本人也被任命为“德国公路系统总监”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国最初修建的高速公路并没有像现在高速公路中间那样显著的隔离装置。按照许多高速公路设计，在战争中把德国高速公路的间隔离填平可以用做飞机跑道。但在二战期间由于盟军轰炸对德国公路系统的破坏以及德国飞机产量不足，这个设计考虑基本没有成为现实。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">历史学者认为，纳粹德国高速公路的军事目的往往被夸大。二战期间德军运输并不依赖于高速公路，特别是战争后期由于燃料缺乏，德军越来越多依靠骡马而非汽车。反而是盟军开进德国后大量使用高速公路系统。</p><p><br/></p>','世界最早的封闭高速公路系统诞生于德国，但是现在世界上规模最大的高速公路系统在中国。德国高速公路以没有限速而闻','新闻',1,3,'images/20180407234325_37.jpg');
